---
// Deep dive: Parallel Agent Management section
---

<section id="agents" class="py-20 md:py-32 relative overflow-hidden">
  <!-- Accent glow -->
  <div class="absolute left-0 top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-[500px] h-[500px] bg-purple/5 rounded-full blur-[150px] pointer-events-none"></div>

  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6">
    <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
      <!-- Left: Screenshot placeholder -->
      <div class="order-2 lg:order-1 animate-on-scroll">
        <div class="relative">
          <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-purple/10 to-cyan/5 rounded-2xl blur-xl scale-105"></div>
          <div class="relative rounded-2xl border border-border overflow-hidden bg-bg-surface shadow-xl">
            <!-- macOS title bar -->
            <div class="flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-3 bg-bg-elevated border-b border-border">
              <div class="flex gap-2">
                <div class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-red/80"></div>
                <div class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-orange/80"></div>
                <div class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-green/80"></div>
              </div>
              <span class="text-xs text-text-muted ml-2 font-mono">Terminal — feature/auth-flow</span>
            </div>
            
            <!-- Terminal mockup with tabs -->
            <div class="flex items-center gap-1 px-3 py-2 bg-bg-elevated/50 border-b border-border">
              <div class="px-3 py-1 rounded-md bg-bg text-xs text-text-primary font-mono border border-border">Shell</div>
              <div class="px-3 py-1 rounded-md text-xs text-cyan font-mono bg-cyan/10 border border-cyan/20 flex items-center gap-1.5">
                <svg width="10" height="10" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M12 2L2 7l10 5 10-5-10-5zM2 17l10 5 10-5M2 12l10 5 10-5"/></svg>
                Claude Agent
              </div>
              <div class="px-3 py-1 rounded-md text-xs text-purple font-mono bg-purple/10 border border-purple/20 flex items-center gap-1.5">
                <svg width="10" height="10" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M12 2L2 7l10 5 10-5-10-5zM2 17l10 5 10-5M2 12l10 5 10-5"/></svg>
                Copilot
              </div>
              <button class="ml-1 w-6 h-6 rounded-md text-text-muted hover:bg-bg-hover flex items-center justify-center">
                <svg width="12" height="12" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><line x1="12" y1="5" x2="12" y2="19"/><line x1="5" y1="12" x2="19" y2="12"/></svg>
              </button>
            </div>

            <!-- Terminal content -->
            <div class="p-4 font-mono text-xs leading-6 h-[320px] bg-bg">
              <div class="text-text-muted">$ claude --model sonnet "Review the auth flow implementation"</div>
              <div class="mt-3">
                <span class="text-cyan">⟩</span> <span class="text-text-primary">Analyzing auth flow in</span> <span class="text-accent">src/auth/</span><span class="text-text-primary">...</span>
              </div>
              <div class="mt-2">
                <span class="text-cyan">⟩</span> <span class="text-text-primary">Found 3 files to review:</span>
              </div>
              <div class="text-text-secondary ml-4 mt-1">
                <div>• <span class="text-green">AuthService.swift</span> — OAuth flow implementation</div>
                <div>• <span class="text-green">KeychainManager.swift</span> — Token storage</div>
                <div>• <span class="text-green">LoginViewModel.swift</span> — UI state management</div>
              </div>
              <div class="mt-3">
                <span class="text-cyan">⟩</span> <span class="text-text-primary">Suggestions:</span>
              </div>
              <div class="text-text-secondary ml-4 mt-1">
                <div><span class="text-orange">⚠</span> Token refresh logic should handle concurrent requests</div>
                <div><span class="text-green">✓</span> Keychain usage follows best practices</div>
                <div><span class="text-green">✓</span> Error states properly propagated to UI</div>
              </div>
              <div class="mt-4 flex items-center">
                <span class="text-green">❯</span>
                <span class="ml-2 w-2 h-4 bg-text-primary animate-pulse"></span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Right: Text content -->
      <div class="order-1 lg:order-2 animate-on-scroll delay-2">
        <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1 rounded-full border border-purple/20 bg-purple/5 text-purple text-xs font-medium mb-6">
          <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <path d="M12 2L2 7l10 5 10-5-10-5z" /><path d="M2 17l10 5 10-5" /><path d="M2 12l10 5 10-5" />
          </svg>
          AI Agent Integration
        </div>

        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold mb-6 leading-tight">
          Run AI agents<br />
          <span class="text-purple">per worktree.</span>
        </h2>

        <p class="text-text-secondary text-lg mb-8 leading-relaxed">
          Attach LLM profiles to terminal sessions and run AI agents in parallel across your worktrees. 
          Each agent operates in its own isolated environment — no cross-contamination.
        </p>

        <ul class="space-y-4">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <div class="w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-purple/10 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">
              <svg width="12" height="12" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#A569E0" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12" /></svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <span class="font-medium text-text-primary">LLM Profiles</span>
              <p class="text-sm text-text-secondary mt-0.5">Configure named profiles for different AI agents — Claude, Copilot, local models. Each profile stores its invocation command.</p>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <div class="w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-purple/10 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">
              <svg width="12" height="12" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#A569E0" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12" /></svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <span class="font-medium text-text-primary">Multi-tab terminals</span>
              <p class="text-sm text-text-secondary mt-0.5">Run multiple terminal sessions per worktree via tmux. Mix shell tabs with AI agent tabs — switch between them instantly.</p>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <div class="w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-purple/10 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">
              <svg width="12" height="12" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#A569E0" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12" /></svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <span class="font-medium text-text-primary">Per-worktree isolation</span>
              <p class="text-sm text-text-secondary mt-0.5">Each worktree has its own terminal environment. Agents work on the correct branch context without interference.</p>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <div class="w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-purple/10 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">
              <svg width="12" height="12" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#A569E0" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12" /></svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <span class="font-medium text-text-primary">GPU-accelerated rendering</span>
              <p class="text-sm text-text-secondary mt-0.5">Powered by Ghostty's Metal-based terminal engine. Buttery smooth scrolling even with verbose agent output.</p>
            </div>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
